Name: PUZZLE: ULTIMATE
About the game: PUZZLE: ULTIMATE - a logic game, the task of which is to assemble puzzles of various sizes. Features: Simple controls (mouse) 30 free levels and a large number of constantly replenishing DLCs (free and paid) Relaxing soundtrack. Beautiful images. Gameplay for all ages. Ability to select a number of puzzles (in the settings menu) from 25 to 225. Credits: Programming: AFBIK Studio Music and effects: zapsplat Pictures: Internet
